Centrotherm Plans No Acquisitions, CFO Tells Boersen-Zeitung

-- B y   A n d r e a s   C r e m e r
-- 
2011-07-30T09:16:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-30/centrotherm-plans-no-acquisitions-cfo-tells-boersen-zeitung.html
Centrotherm Photovoltaics AG (CTN)  has no
plans to make acquisitions to boost growth,  Boersen-Zeitung 
reported, citing Chief Financial Officer Thomas Riegler.  “In our core business we want to grow mainly
organically,” the newspaper quoted the CFO as saying in an
interview published online today. “Acquisitions to capture
market share are out of the question for us.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andreas Cremer in Berlin at 
 acremer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chad Thomas at   cthomas16@bloomberg.net  